'''克里斯·科尼'''（Christopher "Chris" Coyne，{{bd|1978年|12月20日|catIdx=Coyne,Chris}}）是前[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]足球运动员，司职[[后卫_(足球)|后卫]]，现在为澳大利亚球队[[珀斯光荣足球俱乐部|珀斯光荣]]青年軍教練。

==俱乐部生涯==
===早期生涯===
科尼在澳大利亚球队{{tsl|en|Perth SC||珀斯SC}}开始足球生涯。1996年1月，他以2万[[英镑|英镑]]的身价加盟[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]球队[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|西汉姆联]]<ref>[http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-61282354.html Fall-in the foreign legion] {{Wayback|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-61282354.html |date=20121025205934 }}{{en}}</ref>。在西汉姆联队的三年半时间中，他只为西汉姆联出场一次，并在1998年和1999年先后被租借到低级别球队[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|布伦特福德]]和[[绍森德足球俱乐部|绍森德]]锻炼<ref>[http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=128 Games played by Chris Coyne in 1998/1999] {{Wayback|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=128 |date=20080117035328 }}{{en}}</ref>。

2000年3月，科尼自由转会到[[苏格兰足球超级联赛|苏格兰足球超级联赛]]球队[[邓迪足球俱乐部|邓迪]]<ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2182553,00.html Coyne signs for Dundee] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2182553,00.html |date=20161101102335 }}{{en}}</ref>，并在8月份首次代表球队出场<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/dundee/891633.stm Dundee snap up del Rio]{{en}}</ref>。在2000-01赛季中，他在各项比赛中总共为邓迪队出场28次，其中联赛出场20次<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397 |title=Chris Coyne |access-date=2010-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080117035328/http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397 |archive-date=2008-01-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===卢顿===
2001年，[[英格兰足球乙级联赛|英格兰丙级联赛]](第四级别)球队[[卢顿足球俱乐部|卢顿]]以50万英镑的价格买入科尼<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/1515889.stm Coyne and Tweed leave]{{en}}</ref>。虽然他在第一次联赛亮相中打进一个[[乌龙球|乌龙球]]<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/1545875.stm Luton 1-1 Lincoln]{{en}}</ref>，但仍然凭借稳定的表现占据了球队首发位置，除了在01年12月因膝盖韧带受伤错过几场联赛外<ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2225815,00.html Knee woe for Coyne] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2225815,00.html |date=20160815054902 }}{{en}}</ref>，他在整个赛季出场31次<ref>[http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=131 Games played by Chris Coyne in 2001/2002] {{Wayback|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=131 |date=20080117035328 }}{{en}}</ref>，帮助卢顿获得队史最佳的12连胜纪录并最终以第二名的成绩升级到[[英格兰足球甲级联赛|英格兰乙级联赛]](第三级别)<ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2002/apr/08/sport.matthughes Luton hit the top]{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/1899026.stm Swansea 1-3 Luton] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/1899026.stm |date=20060512130409 }}{{en}}</ref>。

科尼在随后两个赛季仍然是球队不可缺少的主力球队，总共为卢顿出场接近100次<ref>[http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=132 Games played by Chris Coyne in 2002/2003] {{Wayback|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=132 |date=20080117035328 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=133 Games played by Chris Coyne in 2003/2004] {{Wayback|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=133 |date=20080117035328 }}{{en}}</ref>，并在2004年5月接受球队的开价，和卢顿续约两年<ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2300020,00.html Duo stay with Hatters] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2300020,00.html |date=20160117014758 }}{{en}}</ref>。卢顿在获得甲级联赛冠军(2004年乙级联赛更名为甲级联赛)<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/4451413.stm Wrexham 1-2 Luton] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/4451413.stm |date=20191214134254 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11702_2333416,00.html League One round-up] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11702_2333416,00.html |date=20160304213744 }}{{en}}</ref>，科尼的表现更是可圈可点，整个赛季联赛出场44次<ref>[http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=134 Games played by Chris Coyne in 2004/2005] {{Wayback|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=12397&seasonid=134 |date=20080117035328 }}{{en}}</ref> ，不但在四月份当选为该月联赛最佳球员<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4506183.stm Trio are handed awards for April] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120717084152/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4506183.stm |date=2012-07-17 }}{{en}}</ref>，而且还入选赛季英甲联赛最佳阵容<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4475213.stm Sunderland/Wigan dominate line-up] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4475213.stm |date=20060219073040 }}{{en}}</ref>。

但在随后的赛季科尼却受到伤病的困扰，最终在2006年4月接受手术治疗，提前告别2005-06赛季<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/luton_town/4895414.stm Luton defender is out for season] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/luton_town/4895414.stm |date=20061219143036 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2373017,00.html Coyne out for season] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2373017,00.html |date=20160117014757 }}{{en}}</ref>。2006年8月，科尼再次和卢顿续约三年<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/luton_town/5256112.stm Coyne and Davis sign new deals] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/luton_town/5256112.stm |date=20080116085546 }}{{en}}</ref>，并当选为球队的新队长。但由于膝伤复发，他在10月份再次接受手术<ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2387643,00.html Hatters eye Coyne replacement] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2387643,00.html |date=20160303224138 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2392231,00.html Luton lose skipper to surgery] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11717_2392231,00.html |date=20160303231914 }}{{en}}</ref> ，直到后半赛季才复出。2007-08赛季，卢顿因被要求债务重组而被监管。为了解决球队的财政困难，卢顿在2008年1月以35万英镑的价格将科尼卖给[[英格兰足球冠军联赛|英格兰足球冠军联赛]]球队[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|科尔切斯特联]]，这个价格也创下科尔切斯特联的球会纪录<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/luton_town/7181317.stm Five players leave troubled Luton] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/luton_town/7181317.stm |date=20170827221904 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_3037062,00.html Coyne seals U's switch] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_3037062,00.html |date=20170322203041 }}{{en}}</ref>。

===离开卢顿后===
虽然科尔切斯特联主教练对科尼寄以厚望，但科尼仍然无法帮助球队在当赛季保级，科尔切斯特联以联赛最后一名的成绩降入甲级联赛<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/7339988.stm Colchester relegation confirmed] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/7339988.stm |date=20080414040240 }}{{en}}</ref>。虽然在2008-09赛季他被任命为球队队长<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/7533777.stm Coyne handed U's captaincy role] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/7533777.stm |date=20220212133552 }}{{en}}</ref>，但由于国家队比赛、受伤、教练的更换等原因，他无法在球队保证主力位置<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/8097705.stm Lambert can understand Coyne view]{{en}}</ref>。2009年7月，他和科尔切斯特联解除合同<ref>[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11702_5423377,00.html Us part with Coyne] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11702_5423377,00.html |date=20160117014757 }}{{en}}</ref>。随后科尼回到[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]，加盟[[珀斯光荣足球俱乐部|珀斯光荣]]<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/07/10/2622936.htm Socceroos defender Coyne joins Glory]{{en}}</ref>。

2010年1月，科尼来到[[中国|中国]]，接受[[中国足球超级联赛|中国足球超级联赛]]球队[[山东鲁能|山东鲁能]]的试训<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sports.sohu.com/20100112/n269509082.shtml |title=伊万否定立陶宛外援 一澳洲铁卫将试训鲁能泰山 |accessdate=2010-01-13 |archive-date=2010-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100115223103/http://sports.sohu.com/20100112/n269509082.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但没有获得山东队的合同，后来转而租借加盟[[辽宁足球俱乐部|辽宁宏运]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/j/2010-03-03/20044867835.shtml |title=辽足斥资千万引英超德甲战将 澳国脚曾欲加盟鲁能 |accessdate=2010-03-04 |archive-date=2010-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100307231336/http://sports.sina.com.cn/j/2010-03-03/20044867835.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在[[2010年中国足球超级联赛|2010赛季中超联赛]]出场20次，赛季结束后回归珀斯光荣。

==国家队生涯==
[[Image:Chris_Coyne.jpg|right]]的训练]]
2008年6月，科尼被召入[[澳大利亚国家足球队|澳大利亚国家队]]以备战[[2010年世界杯外围赛_(亚洲区)|2010年世界杯外围赛]]<ref>[http://www.colchester.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=111481 Coyne in Latest Aussie Squad] {{Wayback|url=http://www.colchester.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=111481 |date=20080628022907 }}{{en}}</ref>，并在客场0比1不敌[[伊拉克国家足球队|伊拉克]]的比赛中首次代表国家队出场。

